title: Volunteer charity workshop leader a champion for seniors (Wanneroo City Council)
text: ( Source : Wanneroo City Council ) Charity worker Brother Olly Pickett has been honoured at the 2015 Seniors Awards for his work at the Wangara workshop 'Wheelchairs for Kids '. Brother Pickett was awarded the Juniper Champion for Seniors
